<h4>Proper Use</h4>
Prepare (or select existing) images (950px wide, 335px high) to rotate through on the main page. You can select as many images as you like. They will rotate in the order listed.
<p>If you do not specify any images, that image space is not displayed and the rest of the page shifts up.</p>
<p>These images are showcases for your department. They should be updated or replaced several times a year-ideally, at least one image changed each month.</p>
<p>If you need fresh images, please contact Academic Technology Services. Jeff Smith may already have a selection, or his team may come for a photo shoot.</p>
